OL,3,CWhat is the two-child benefit cap and
OL,4,Chow many kids does it impact?
OL,6,FThe two-child benefit cap was
OL,7,Fintroduced in 2015 by the
OL,8,FConservatives and came into effect in
OL,9,F2017.
OL,11,FIt restricts the child tax credit and
OL,12,Funiversal credit (UC) to the first two
OL,13,Fchildren in most households, and only
OL,14,Fapplies to children who were born
OL,15,Fafter 6 April 2017.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
