OL,7,Fthe average income is defined as
OL,8,Fliving in "deep poverty."
OL,10,FThe Child Poverty Action Group also
OL,11,Fsays that 59% of families affected by
OL,12,Fthe cap have at least one parent in
OL,13,Fwork - arguing the suggestion that the
OL,14,Fcap encourages parents on benefits to
OL,15,Fwork is unsupported by evidence.
