OL,6,FIn September this year, Badenoch said:
OL,7,F"I am committing now that if the two-
OL,8,Fchild cap is lifted, the next
OL,9,FConservative government will reinstate
OL,10,Fit, because we believe in fairness and
OL,11,Fthat people on benefits should make
OL,12,Fthe same responsible decisions about
OL,13,Fhaving children as everyone else."
OL,15,FThere has been some confusion about
OL,16,FReform UK's position on the policy,
OL,17,Fafter Nigel Farage said in May he
OL,18,Fsupported the idea of it being
OL,19,Fscrapped in order to encourage
OL,20,Ffamilies to have more children.
