OL,6,FWhy do charities also want the overall
OL,7,Fcap on benefits lifted?
OL,9,FWhile families, campaigners and many
OL,10,FLabour MPs are pleased that the two-
OL,11,Fchild limit appears set to be
OL,12,Fscrapped, there are fears the move
OL,13,Fcould see families hit by a second
OL,14,Fbenefit limit.
OL,16,FThe overall cap on benefits limits the
OL,17,Famount of money working age households
OL,18,Fon benefits can receive - it's
OL,19,Fcurrently set at #22,000 a year
OL,20,Foutside London and impacts around
OL,21,F120,000 households.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/18
